<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Yarım Sayfa Carousel</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
       

            .carousel-item img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                object-fit: cover;
                border-radius:25px;
            }

        .content {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

            .content h1, .content p {
                margin: 0 0 20px;
                padding: 0 50px;
                text-align: center;
            }

        .split-left {
            left: 0;
            width: 50%;
        }

        .split-right {
            right: 0;
            width: 50%;
        }
        .card-img {
            object-fit: cover; /* Resmi kutuya sığdır */
            width: 100%; /* Resmi sütun genişliğine uydur */
            height: 100%; /* Yüksekliği sabit tut */
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem; /* Başlık boyutunu büyüt */
            margin-bottom: 0; /* Alt boşluğu kaldır */
        }

        .card-body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column; /* İçerikleri dikey olarak hizala */
            justify-content: center; /* İçerikleri ortala */
            align-items: start; /* İçerikleri sol tarafa yasla */
            padding: 1.25rem; /* İç boşluğu ekle */
            text-align: left; /* Metni sola hizala */
        }
        .context-body{
            display: flex;
            margin-top:-40px;
            background: #f7f7f7;
        }
        .context-body-left{
            margin-top:250px;
            margin-left:15%;
            margin-right:15%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="context-body">
        <div class="split-left ">
            <div class="context-body-left">
                <h1 id="carousel-heading">Building   Beyond Boundaries</h1>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Officia, error quam dolorem inventore eveniet sit et amet dolor explicabo vero repudiandae mollitia quidem, earum libero vitae dolore dolores blanditiis ullam!</p>
                <div class="container mt-5">
                    <div class="">
                        <img width="50%" src="~/images/Screenshot 2024-03-30 150210.png" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


        </div>

        <div class="split-right">
            <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <img src="~/images/Ekran görüntüsü 2024-03-24 222005.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Mimari">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="~/images/Ekran görüntüsü 2024-03-24 222023.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Mimari">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="~/images/Ekran görüntüsü 2024-03-24 222034.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Mimari">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        var carouselTexts = [
            {
                heading: "Building   Beyond Boundaries",
            },
            {
                heading: "Turning Ideas into Digital Reality",
            },
            {
                heading: "Secure Your Trust,Project Your Future!",
            }
        ];

        $('#carouselExampleControls').on('slid.bs.carousel', function (event) {
            var currentIndex = $('.carousel-item.active').index();
            var currentText = carouselTexts[currentIndex];
            $('#carousel-heading').text(currentText.heading);
            $('#carousel-text').text(currentText.text);
            $('#carousel-projects').text(currentText.projects);
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
